---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AffiliateCTA from '../../components/AffiliateCTA.astro';
import { AFFILIATE_LINKS as affiliates } from '../../config/affiliate-links';

const title = 'AI Website Builder Content Strategy (2025)';
const description = 'AI generates the structure, but what about content? Here is how to create effective content for AI-generated sites.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold mb-4">GUIDE</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">AI Website Builder Content Strategy</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
        AI builds the site. You build the content. Here is what actually works.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">The Truth About AI Content</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg">
        AI-generated copy is a <strong>starting point</strong>, not finished work. It lacks personality, specifics, and human touch.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Best approach:</strong> Use AI for structure, write content yourself (or heavily edit AI output).
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Content AI Does Well</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Page Structure</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            AI is great at determining what pages you need (home, about, services, contact) and what sections go on each page.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Basic Copy Framework</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Headlines, subheadlines, benefit lists - AI generates reasonable first drafts you can refine.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Meta Data</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Page titles, meta descriptions, alt text - AI handles these adequately.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Content AI Does Poorly</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Personality & Voice</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            AI writing sounds generic and robotic. Your brand has a personality - AI can't capture it without significant prompting and editing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Specific Details</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            AI generates vague content ("We provide excellent service"). Great content includes specifics ("We respond within 2 hours, 24/7").
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">4. Stories & Examples</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Real customer stories, case studies, examples - AI can't invent these. Only you can provide authentic proof.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">5. Industry Nuance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            AI knows generalities, not industry-specific insights. Your expertise is what makes content valuable.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Hybrid Strategy: AI + Human</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <strong>Best approach:</strong> Let AI build structure and draft copy. Then heavily edit with your voice.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-6 mb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">
            <strong>Content workflow:</strong> AI generates → You review → You add personality → You add specifics → You add proof → Publish
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-700">
          This 5-step workflow takes 1-2 hours per page but produces content that actually converts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Essential Pages (What to Say)</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Homepage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Must include:</strong> Clear value proposition, what you do, who it's for, social proof, and call-to-action.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">About Page</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Must include:</strong> Your story, why you started, what makes you different, team photos, values.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Services/Products</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Must include:</strong> Clear description, pricing (transparent), what's included, expected outcomes, FAQs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Contact</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Must include:</strong> Multiple contact methods, response time expectation, location (if relevant), form.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Content Quality Checklist</h2>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>Does it sound like a human wrote it?</li>
        <li>Are there specific examples and details?</li>
        <li>Is there proof (testimonials, case studies)?</li>
        <li>Does it reflect your brand voice?</li>
        <li>Is it clear what action to take next?</li>
        <li>Would YOU trust this site if you were a customer?</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <AffiliateCTA
        href={affiliates['10web'].affiliateUrl}
        commission={affiliates['10web'].commission}
        label="Start Building with 10Web"
        className="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg inline-block"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Related Reviews -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-[#F5521A]"></div>Related Reviews
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/reviews/framer-ai" class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 border-[3px] border-gray-200 hover:border-[#F5521A] transition-all group">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-black text-white">9.3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#F5521A] mb-1">Framer AI</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Best CMS for content sites. Blog-optimized structure.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/reviews/10web-ai" class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 border-[3px] border-gray-200 hover:border-[#F5521A] transition-all group">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-black text-white">8.4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#F5521A] mb-1">10Web AI</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">WordPress foundation. Best blogging platform.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/reviews/webflow-ai" class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 border-[3px] border-gray-200 hover:border-[#F5521A] transition-all group">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-600 to-slate-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-black text-white">CMS</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#F5521A] mb-1">Webflow</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Powerful CMS. Full content control and structure.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/reviews/squarespace-ai" class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 border-[3px] border-gray-200 hover:border-[#F5521A] transition-all group">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-700 to-gray-900 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-black text-white">8.7</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#F5521A] mb-1">Squarespace AI</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Beautiful blog templates. Easy content management.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
